## TELECOMMUNICATION & VOICE SERVICES DISCLAIMER

**IMPORTANT: This software is for educational and demonstration purposes.**

### Service Requirements

This voice assistant system:

- Requires active Twilio account and valid credentials
- Requires AWS account for Polly text-to-speech services
- May incur charges from third-party service providers
- Requires compliance with telecommunication regulations

### Usage Restrictions

Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining proper Twilio and AWS credentials
- Complying with TCPA (Telephone Consumer Protection Act)
- Following telemarketing and robocalling regulations
- Respecting Do Not Call registries
- Obtaining consent before making automated calls
- Ensuring GDPR and privacy law compliance

### Legal Compliance

- Automated calling systems must comply with local laws
- Users must obtain consent for recording calls
- Voice data must be handled according to privacy regulations
- Healthcare appointments require HIPAA compliance
- Financial services require additional security measures

### Liability Waiver

The authors and contributors:
- Disclaim all liability for service charges
- Make no guarantees of service availability
- Assume no responsibility for regulatory violations
- Provide no warranty for production deployment

**REGULATORY NOTICE:** Automated calling and voice systems are subject to federal and state regulations. Ensure compliance with all applicable laws before deployment.